            <tr><td>Sunday</td><td>Rest</td><td>Full rest day</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <p>This level of training requires years of progressive development. Start with the <a href="/beginner-deadhang/">beginner dead hang program</a> and work through the <a href="/deadhang-progressions/">full progression ladder</a> before attempting advanced protocols.</p>

        <h2 id="your-level">How You Compare to the World Record</h2>
        <p>The gap between an average dead hang and the world record is enormous. Here is how common performance levels stack up against the 80:41 record.</p>

        <table class="data-table">
